name: Love Language
description:
There was this beautiful young lady in Senggarang Village.⁣
She spoke in Hokkien, and I honestly understood none of⁣
everything she said at that time. But she kept smiling while ⁣
talking, and since then I believe that every word came out⁣
from her mouth must be lovely.⁣
⁣
After insisting to communicate to each other with our own⁣
language, I put my shades on her and she didn't mind at all..❤️⁣
⁣
-⁣
⁣
I lost my camera the day after I took this picture,⁣
this is the only copy I have on my phone.⁣
